 - Maintain a parallel directory of MP3 files
 - Treat MP3 file with no corresponding source as an orphan, and delete
 - Configure with YAML
 - Maintain "view" directories which are links back to source / MP3
 - Keep view directories in sync with source
 - Allow file name format to be configured
 - Use a thread pool to allow parallel (but constrained) transcoding
 - Allow drop handlers to be configured (e.g., Tivo handler needs media key)
 - Document external dependencies (including how to build flac)
 - Document how to write a drop handler, media tag handler
 - Handlers for TiVo files, VOB files
 - iTunes integration
